Description.Name: Basic Attack: Frost Petal Dance
Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Heavy Strike
Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Crash Strike
Description.Desc:
Seed has <color=#FFFFFF>Steel Charge</color>, which can be restored when her skills hit enemies.
<color=#FFFFFF>Steel Charge</color> has a maximum of 150 points and starts at 60 points. When above 120 points, after activating Falling Petals - Slaughter, press or hold <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to consume 120 points of <color=#FFFFFF>Steel Charge</color> to unleash Falling Petals - Downfall, dealing massive <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color> to finish off enemies.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Heavy Strike
Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Crash Strike I
Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Crash Strike II
Dodge: Petal Dance
Dash Attack: Magnetic Meteor Dance
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a dodge to activate:
Throws a high-speed steel wheel forward, dealing <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.

Description.Name: Dodge Counter: Blooming Splendor
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a <color=#FFFFFF>Perfect Dodge</color> to activate:
Unleashes a barrage of shots at enemies in front, dealing <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Special Attack: Frost Fall
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
Throw a steel wheel that deals <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color> along a curved path.

Description.Name: EX Special Attack: Iron Petal Storm
EX Special Attack: Raining Iron Petals - Away
Description.Desc:
During Raining Iron Petals, release <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to activate:
Unleash rapid cannon fire, dealing small <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: EX Special Attack: Iron Petal Storm
EX Special Attack: Iron Petal Storm
Chain Attack: Hailstorm Storm
Ultimate: Clockwork Garden - Bloom!
Description.Desc:
When Decibel Rating is at <color=#FFFFFF>Maximum</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_UltimateReady> to activate:
Enter mech mode and unleash a barrage of attacks on enemies ahead in first-person view, followed by a devastating slam attack, dealing massive <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.
After using this skill, recover 60 <color=#FFFFFF>Steel Charge</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Quick Assist: Petal Storm
Description.Desc:
When the active character is launched, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Unleashes a barrage of shots at enemies in front, dealing <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Defensive Assist: Chuhua Barrier
Description.Desc:
When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Parries the enemy's attack, accumulating massive Daze.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Assist Follow-Up: Crimson Core Burst
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>Defensive Assist</color> to activate:
Unleashes a series of floating turret attacks at enemies ahead, dealing <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Name: Core Passive: Flower Chain Protocol
Additional Ability: Surprise Strike
Desc:
The Attack teammate with the highest ATK is considered Seed's <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color>.
When the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color> unleashes an <color=#FFFFFF>EX Special Attack</color>, Seed gains <color=#FFFFFF>Onslaught</color>, increasing Seed's ATK by <color=#2BAD00>100</color> and CRIT DMG by <color=#2BAD00>15%</color>. When Seed unleashes an <color=#FFFFFF>EX Special Attack</color>, the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color> gains <color=#FFFFFF>Direct Strike</color> status, increasing the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color>'s ATK by <color=#2BAD00>100</color> and CRIT DMG by <color=#2BAD00>15%</color>.
When <color=#FFFFFF>Direct Strike</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>Onslaught</color> are both active, Seed and the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color> simultaneously gain <color=#FFFFFF>Besiege</color>, increasing all DMG dealt by <color=#2BAD00>15%</color>.
<color=#FFFFFF>Onslaught</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>Direct Strike</color>, and <color=#FFFFFF>Besiege</color> can all take effect when the character is the current active character. When becoming inactive, the effects remain until the character goes off-field or 3 seconds after the switch.
Upon entering a stage, Seed immediately gains <color=#FFFFFF>Onslaught</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>Besiege</color>, while the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color> immediately gains <color=#FFFFFF>Direct Strike</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>Besiege</color>.
<color=#FFFFFF>Direct Strike</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>Onslaught</color> status last for 40s, and repeated triggers refresh the duration.
When the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color> consumes Energy as the active character or when Seed consumes Energy, for every 1 point of Energy consumed, Seed recovers 0.5 points of <color=#FFFFFF>Steel Charge</color>.

When another Attack Character is in your squad:
When Seed deals DMG as the active character, restore 2 Energy to the <color=#FFFFFF>Vanguard</color>. This effect can trigger once every 1s.
Seed's <color=#FFFFFF>Falling Petals - Slaughter</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>Falling Petals - Downfall</color>, and <color=#FFFFFF>Clockwork Garden - Bloom!</color> deal <color=#2BAD00>30%</color> increased All-Attribute DMG and ignore <color=#2BAD00>25%</color> of enemy RES.

1.Name: "Hibernation Period"
1.Desc: Reduces <color=#FFFFFF>[Steel Charge]</color> consumed by <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Crash Strike I]</color> to 100; gain additional 40/20 <color=#FFFFFF>[Steel Charge]</color> when entering the battlefield/activating <color=#FFFFFF>[Ultimate]</color>; increases <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Crash Strike]</color>'s CRIT DMG by 30%.

2.Name: "Light Absorption"
2.Desc: When activating <color=#FFFFFF>[Ultimate: Clockwork Garden - Bloom!]</color>, increases the Daze duration of all Stunned enemies by 4 seconds. Each enemy can only be affected once during a single Daze period, and similar effects cannot stack. While under <color=#FFFFFF>[Besiege]</color> status, Agents ignore 15% of enemy DEF when dealing DMG.

4.Name: "Aromatic Notes"
4.Desc: When <color=#FFFFFF>[Besiege]</color> is active, Seed's Decibel Generation Rate increases by 10%, and <color=#FFFFFF>[Ultimate]</color> DMG increases by 15%.

6.Name: "Theory of Mind"
6.Desc:
Seed's CRIT DMG increases by 50%;
When casting <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Falling Petals - Heavy Strike]</color>, fires 3 additional laser beams, each dealing 165% of ATK as DMG. This effect can trigger once every 3 seconds.
